# Build Artifacts Management

## Release Files Only
Only include actual plugin files in releases. Exclude all build artifacts and intermediate files.

### Allowed Release Files:
- **macOS**: `Pulse24Sync.vst3`, `Pulse24Sync.component`, `Pulse24Sync.app`
- **Windows**: `Pulse24Sync.vst3`, `Pulse24Sync.exe`

### Excluded Files:
- `juce_vst3_helper` - JUCE build helper (not user-facing)
- `libPulse24Sync.a` - Static library (build artifact)
- `*.pdb` - Debug symbols
- `*.obj`, `*.lib` - Intermediate build files
- `*.tmp`, `*.temp` - Temporary files
- `.vs/`, `*.build/` - IDE/build directories

## Build Path Configuration
In [.github/workflows/release.yml](mdc:.github/workflows/release.yml), use specific file paths, not wildcards:
```yaml
build-path: |
  Builds/MacOSX/build/Release/Pulse24Sync.vst3
  Builds/MacOSX/build/Release/Pulse24Sync.component
  Builds/MacOSX/build/Release/Pulse24Sync.app
```

## Cleanup
Always clean up build artifacts after successful builds to prevent repository bloat.
